Stage 8 of 8: Renown and Rebirth, level 100 and beyond

At level 100 your level becomes renown: HERO, ADV, or VILN by your
deeds. Level 150 makes you a LEGEND and unlocks a free mythic-guild
character.

At 250 the true endgame opens: remort, a rebirth that trades your
level for permanent boon points and starts the climb again, stronger
each cycle. Specialization and the metaphysician path round out a
veteran's power.

